gst.signalprocessing

Class LiveSignalProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • gst.signalprocessing.SignalProcessor
      • gst.signalprocessing.LiveSignalProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataChangeListener, java.util.EventListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RRLiveCalculator

    public abstract class LiveSignalProcessor
extends SignalProcessor
implements DataChangeListener
    This SignalProcessor reacts on data changes on its source signals and accordingly modifies the targeted signals. This behavior can be enabled an disabled by the start() and stop() methods.
    Version:
    0.0.0.1 (16.10.2012)
    Author:
    Enrico Grunitz
